definitions.body: [[ישׁה]] (√ of following; meaning uncertain; acc. Fl De:Pr 2:7 = Ar. 0’asa0, III. 0a0san0, var. wa0sa0, assist, support: nut this dubious; v. Lane:60 )cf. Wetzst:ZDMG 1868, 119) acc. to whom this is a second. sense from to make equal (viz. by giving to another of one's own property, etc.))
